<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 16:09:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>精疲力竭的黎巴嫩无法对真主党发起公民不服从</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/an-exhausted-lebanon-cant-mount-civil-disobedience-against-hezbollah/00000191-9397-d13a-ab93-dbb7aa340000</link><description>黎巴嫩正处于多层面的危机之中，以色列“将其送入石器时代”的威胁遭到了人们的质疑，因为许多黎巴嫩人认为他们已经进入了石器时代。黎巴嫩人民以前也曾奋起反抗，但真主党装备精良、支持充足，难以受到挑战</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:23:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/news/middle-east/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/an-exhausted-lebanon-cant-mount-civil-disobedience-against-hezbollah/00000191-9397-d13a-ab93-dbb7aa340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长没有向死者家属道歉，而是决心推进司法政变</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-apologizing-israels-justice-minister-is-set-on-advancing-the-judicial-coup/00000191-93c1-dd8c-addd-bbf5c9750000</link><description>10 月 7 日之后的一段时间里，司法政变策划者亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 显得抑郁而孤僻。发给他的信息指责他对这次袭击负有直接责任，促使他考虑辞职。然而从那时起，他的脸颊又恢复了颜色</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-apologizing-israels-justice-minister-is-set-on-advancing-the-judicial-coup/00000191-93c1-dd8c-addd-bbf5c9750000</guid></item><item><title>军方称，涉嫌在约旦河西岸谋杀以色列狱警的巴勒斯坦人有民族主义动机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/idf-palestinian-suspected-of-murdering-israeli-prison-guard-had-nationalistic-motives/00000191-9363-da3c-a99b-b7ff0f3a0000</link><description>向军事法庭提交的起诉书称，约旦河西岸 Biddu 村居民易卜拉欣·曼苏尔 (Ibrahim Mansour) 刺伤了以色列监狱看守约海·阿夫尼 (Yohai Avni) 66 刀，谋杀了他。一项修正案补充说，曼苏尔因他是犹太人而杀了他</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 14:03:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/idf-palestinian-suspected-of-murdering-israeli-prison-guard-had-nationalistic-motives/00000191-9363-da3c-a99b-b7ff0f3a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队称在约旦河西岸发动了空袭；巴勒斯坦人报告五人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-it-carried-out-airstrike-in-west-bank-palestinians-report-five-killed/00000191-934f-da3c-a99b-b7ffba2c0000</link><description>以色列军队表示，其飞机袭击了约旦河西岸城市图勒凯尔姆附近努尔沙姆斯难民营的一个武装行动中心</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 12:22:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-it-carried-out-airstrike-in-west-bank-palestinians-report-five-killed/00000191-934f-da3c-a99b-b7ffba2c0000</guid></item><item><title>两家极端正统派报纸谴责本格维尔的圣殿山/阿克萨大院政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/two-ultra-orthodox-newspapers-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound-policy/00000191-9343-df0a-ab9f-f34b8ed00000</link><description>“世世代代所有犹太哈拉奇统治者都认为禁止犹太人登上圣殿山”：正统派报纸 Yated Ne&amp;#39;eman 和 Haderech 都猛烈抨击国家安全部长</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 12:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/two-ultra-orthodox-newspapers-condemn-ben-gvirs-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound-policy/00000191-9343-df0a-ab9f-f34b8ed00000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡正在利用美国大选来制造混乱并操纵以色列公众”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-27/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-is-using-the-u-s-election-to-feed-chaos-and-manipulate-the-israeli-public/00000191-931c-dd8c-addd-bbfc781a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 12:15:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-08-27/ty-article-podcast/netanyahu-is-using-the-u-s-election-to-feed-chaos-and-manipulate-the-israeli-public/00000191-931c-dd8c-addd-bbfc781a0000</guid></item><item><title>当极端正统说唱歌手在 Mea She&amp;#39;arim 中吐出热火时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-ultra-orthodox-men-drop-fire-bars-in-the-mea-shearim-hood/00000191-92de-d466-a799-fbff251d0000</link><description>新社交媒体系列“Mea Shearim Underground”的主角设法弥合了嘻哈抗议文化与新宗教犹太学校之间的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 11:48:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/when-ultra-orthodox-men-drop-fire-bars-in-the-mea-shearim-hood/00000191-92de-d466-a799-fbff251d0000</guid></item><item><title>高等法院要求司法部长在拖延数月后召开司法任命委员会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/high-court-tells-justice-minister-to-convene-judicial-appointments-committee/00000191-9355-dc4a-a59b-b3fd80eb0000</link><description>由于司法部长亚里夫·莱文未能选出最高法院院长或填补法院空缺，高等法院表示任命委员会必须在9月之前召开会议，否则将发布命令</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 11:46:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/high-court-tells-justice-minister-to-convene-judicial-appointments-committee/00000191-9355-dc4a-a59b-b3fd80eb0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党为巴勒斯坦做过什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/what-has-hezbollah-ever-done-for-palestine/00000191-9343-da3c-a99b-b7ff1f0f0000</link><description>真主党对以色列的“抵抗”是一场史诗般的骗局。这是一支暴力、腐败、不合时宜的势力，用每个人的生命玩区域轮盘赌，专门剥削巴勒斯坦事业</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 11:16:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/what-has-hezbollah-ever-done-for-palestine/00000191-9343-da3c-a99b-b7ff1f0f0000</guid></item><item><title>逃离加沙的以色列裔阿拉伯妇女和她的孩子被拒绝进入以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-woman-and-her-children-fleeing-gaza-denied-entry-into-israel/00000191-92fe-d13a-ab93-daffaf920000</link><description>“这是官僚暴力的表现，”参与此案的一名律师说。以色列法律要求进行基因测试来证明母亲和孩子之间的关系，但以色列要求他们留在加沙，直到结果出来</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 10:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-arab-woman-and-her-children-fleeing-gaza-denied-entry-into-israel/00000191-92fe-d13a-ab93-daffaf920000</guid></item><item><title>“新篇​​章”：贝埃里基布兹的居民开始临时搬到哈泽里姆基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-kibbutz-beeri-begin-temporary-move-to-kibbutz-hatzerim-in-southern-israel/00000191-92de-d302-add5-9bded48b0000</link><description>到目前为止，Be&amp;#39;eri 社区已经拥有了南部基布兹专门建造的约 300 套住房中的 60 套。 “与哈泽里姆成员的共同努力……让我们充满希望，”贝埃里基布兹的秘书说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-kibbutz-beeri-begin-temporary-move-to-kibbutz-hatzerim-in-southern-israel/00000191-92de-d302-add5-9bded48b0000</guid></item><item><title>据军方称，巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军预备役军人杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-in-west-bank-by-idf-reservists-according-to-the-army/00000191-92aa-d336-a991-f6fa8bd30000</link><description>根据以色列国防军的初步调查，该男子在与定居者发生冲突后在埃弗拉特定居点附近被以色列预备役军人开枪射杀。一名巴勒斯坦市政负责人却表示，便衣定居者进入村庄并不分青红皂白地开枪</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 08:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-in-west-bank-by-idf-reservists-according-to-the-army/00000191-92aa-d336-a991-f6fa8bd30000</guid></item><item><title>战时条件使加沙儿童脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种项目变得复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/war-time-conditions-complicate-project-to-vaccinate-gazan-children-against-polio/00000191-903e-d302-add5-9bbefc300000</link><description>为约 640,000 名 10 岁以下儿童接种疫苗的计划背后的卫生组织担心，加沙地带的条件将导致疫苗的分发变得困难，因为疫苗需要两剂并需要冷藏</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 03:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/war-time-conditions-complicate-project-to-vaccinate-gazan-children-against-polio/00000191-903e-d302-add5-9bbefc300000</guid></item><item><title>地区战争暂时避免，但军队仍无视以色列北部的现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-cant-prevent-normalized-chaos-in-the-north/00000191-9036-d13a-ab93-d8b740360000</link><description>成功挫败真主党的袭击象征着以色列在 10 月 7 日所严重缺乏的情报和作战优势 ■ 本格维尔对圣殿山的挑衅是一场复杂游戏的一部分 — — 其中一些是与内塔尼亚胡协调的</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-cant-prevent-normalized-chaos-in-the-north/00000191-9036-d13a-ab93-d8b740360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙救出被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-one-killed-three-wounded-by-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank/00000191-91a0-d302-add5-9bb4e4960000</link><description>卫生部报告，五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸空袭中丧生 ■ 军方表示，巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军预备役军人杀害 ■ 美国高级将领表示，以色列与真主党交锋后，更广泛战争的风险略有缓解 ■ 报告：以色列在拉法北部的空袭中造成一人死亡■ 伊朗外长称德黑兰对以色列的反应将是“明确的、经过深思熟虑的和准确的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 02:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-one-killed-three-wounded-by-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank/00000191-91a0-d302-add5-9bb4e4960000</guid></item><item><title>法院规定，必须允许反 LGBTQ、极端正统团体在以色列校园内活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/anti-lgbt-ultra-orthodox-group-must-be-allowed-to-operate-on-israeli-campus-court-rules/00000191-8fc3-d13a-ab93-dff7f75c0000</link><description>在海法地方法院裁定以色列理工学院不能限制反 LGBTQ 选择家庭组织的活动后，该大学表示将“继续采取行动，确保校园安全、包容并支持每个人”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 21:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/anti-lgbt-ultra-orthodox-group-must-be-allowed-to-operate-on-israeli-campus-court-rules/00000191-8fc3-d13a-ab93-dff7f75c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长与高等法院院长就继任者任命发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-clashes-with-high-court-president-over-successors-appointment/00000191-9040-d336-a991-f6d054600000</link><description>司法部长莱文的提议挑战了资历制度，即任职时间最长的法官自动被任命为最高法院院长。莱文称其为“公平妥协”，但批评者称其为“政治和法律暴行”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 20:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-clashes-with-high-court-president-over-successors-appointment/00000191-9040-d336-a991-f6d054600000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普与以色列犹太至上主义者的邪恶联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</link><description>下一届美国总统任期可能是以色列历史上最重要的任期：以色列人和巴勒斯坦人再也无法承受特朗普给内塔尼亚胡的空白支票</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 18:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党袭击未能引发全面战争后，美国看到了以色列与哈马斯谈判的前进方向</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</link><description>拜登政府官员认为，避免以色列与真主党发生广泛冲突会加剧辛瓦尔的孤立和谈判灵活性的压力。然而，关键问题，特别是以色列在加沙-埃及边境的存在仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方因计划放映有关以色列国防军在西岸活动的电影而关闭了阿拉伯犹太党总部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</link><description>警方关闭了哈达什党的海法分部，原因是计划放映一部有关以色列军事活动的电影，他们声称该电影在以色列被禁止——而事实上，以色列法院已禁止放映同一导演于 2002 年创作的一部电影</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</guid></item></channel></rss>